snippet.title: SNAIL FRY | NATHAI VARUVAL | Snail Recipe Cooking and Eating in Village | Healthy Village Recipes
snippet.description:
Discover the art of traditional Snail Fry (Nathai Varuval) cooking in the heart of the village! üêå‚ú® This unique recipe combines fresh, locally sourced snails with a blend of aromatic spices, creating a mouthwatering dish that‚Äôs as healthy as it is flavorful.

Watch as we prepare this delicacy from scratch, using simple yet time-tested techniques over a firewood stove. Every step showcases the charm of village cooking, from cleaning the snails to frying them to perfection.

What‚Äôs in the Recipe:

Fresh snails straight from nature
A medley of traditional spices
Gingelly oil and hand-ground masala for authentic flavor

This video is not just about cooking; it celebrates culture, community, and the joy of sharing delicious food. Stay until the end for a delightful tasting session that will leave you craving this wholesome delicacy!

snippet.title: LIVE : India's Republic Day Parade 26th January, 2025 | ‡§ó‡§£‡§§‡§Ç‡§§‡•ç‡§∞ ‡§¶‡§ø‡§µ‡§∏  | 26 January Parade Live
snippet.description:
India celebrates the 76th Republic Day on 26th January 2025. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 76th Republic Day Parade on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! Today, for the tenth consecutive year, we will LIVE-STREAM the Republic Day Parade. Proud Indians and Indophiles from all over the world will be watching, along with our viewers from the freezing climate of Leh to the remotest corners of Kanyakumari, Thank you for always being with us - Friends of Doordarshan. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan.

snippet.title: FilterCopy | When You Marry Your Exact Opposite | Ft. Ayush Mehra and Barkha Singh
snippet.description:
This Valentine's Day, visit the nearest Mia Store and say you love them with Mia's Joy of Gifting Festival! Available online too: https://bit.ly/40pFWeG

Our favourite on-screen couple is BACK! üíñ Ayush Mehra and Barkha Singh return to FilterCopy, bringing with them the magic that has made them one the most beloved pair in our viewers' hearts. Remember those countless moments when their chemistry made you laugh, cry, and feel every emotion in between? This time, they're diving deep into the hilarious world of being married to your complete opposite!

About the Episode: A soap film can solve some of the most difficult problems of finding the optimum path between cities. Why do bees make hexagons not square or pentagons for their beehives? We will explore optimization properties of natural elements i.e. light, electricity, gravity and see how beautifully natural laws are interconnected.

Topics Covered
Surface Tension, Area and Perimeter, 2D Geometry, 3D Geometry, Mensurations, Snell‚Äôs Law, Reflection, Refraction, Total Internal Reflection, Optics, Cell Structure, Cell Division, Chemistry of Soap, Motion and Algebra, Shortest and Fastest Path,

Having conducted over 200 STEM and hands-on learning workshops for over 20,000 teachers & professors and connected with over 500,000 students nationwide - our mission is to bring back the gleam in their eyes!

snippet.title: Tu Hain Toh Main Hoon | Sky Force | Akshay, Sara, Veer, Tanishk B, Arijit Singh, Afsana Khan, Irshad
snippet.description:
Experience the magic of love with Tu Hai Toh Main Hoon from Sky Force! This soulful melody, sung by Arijit Singh and Afsana Khan, beautifully captures the essence of love and togetherness. Featuring Veer Pahariya and Sara Ali Khan, with lyrics by Irshad Kamil and music by Tanishk Bagchi, this song will surely strike a chord in your heart.

üëâ Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Song Credits:
Song name - Tu Hain Toh Main Hoon
Singer - Arijit Singh , Afsana khan
Music - Tanishk Bagchi 
Lyrics - Irshad kamil
Starcast - Veer Pahariya, Sara Ali Khan
Programming - Tanishk Bagchi
Additional Programming- Krishna Kishore
Drums - Stuart Brown ( Scotland ) 
Guitars - Keba Jeremiah 
Nylon Guitars - Ben (Scotland) 
Rhythm - Krishna Kishor 
Woodwinds - Ashish 
Solo Humming - Kamalaja 
Female - Kamalaja, Sri Radha , Fathima 
Dubbing Engineers - Lijesh & Mani Ratnam
Violin Solo-Jeetendra 
Mix and master - Eric Pillai @ Future Sound Of Bombay
Hookline inspired from Mohsen Yeganeh song ‚ÄúBehet Ghol Midam‚Äù

Movie Credits:
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan
Produced By: Jyoti Deshpande
Produced By: Amar Kaushik
Producer: Sahil Baber Khan
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota, Poonam Shivdasani & Komal Kewlani
Written By: Carl Austin (UK), Sandeep Kewlani and Aamil Keeyan Khan
Additional Screenplay & Dialogues By: Niren Bhatt
Director Of Photography: Santhana Krishanan Ravichandran
Director of Choreography- Vijay Ganguly

Lyrics:-

Subhe subhe subhe subhe teri yaadein
Subhe subhe subhe subhe din bana de
Tu meri kheedkiyo pe bikhre din banke
Tu mujhpe dhoop sa hai girta chan chan ke
Chan chan ke

Tu ishq hai toh main baahon mein hoon
Baahon mein hoon toh panaahon mein hoon
Kajal hoon toh main nigahon mein hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Kasme vaade kyun tu hain toh main hoon
Bas main tera hoon tu hain toh main hoon
Seene pe likh loon tu hain toh main hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Antara:
Ek mutthi khwahishon ki tere aage khol ke
Zindagi bhar chup rahoonga baatein dil ki bol ke
Na tere saaye pe bhi aaye koi aanch dua maangoon
Main sadke main tere apni khushi de doonga tol ke

Tu rang mein, teri pehchaan hoon
Pehchaan hoon, main teri jaan hoon
Main koi tera hi armaan hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Jhoothe Judaiyan
Jhoothe  bichhode
Yaad kisi ka haath na chhode
Yaad kahe yeh humse aksar
Tu hain toh main hoon

snippet.title: Skoda Kylaq Manual & AT Drive Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste, Skoda India is finally shipping their cars to dealerships, and you can buy them. It has been a long wait for many prospective buyers, considering we first saw the car last year, and it is ready, but it is now, in January 2025, that buyers will see it. But no matter what, this is an essential car for Skoda India. It did spark interest in customers when the introductory price was accounted. Here is a detailed video of manual and automatic drivetrains I recorded recently in Goa. 

Timestamps:
00:00 Introduction
00:36 Exteriors, including Looks, Design, Approach Departure angles, Wheels, door, taillights etc
02:09 Interiors including Dashboard, Features, Seats, Space, etc
04:40 Skoda Kylaw Variant Distribution
05:50 Skoda Kylaq rear seat space and issues
08:10 Boot space
09:33 Skoda Kylaq 1 Liter AT drive Impressions
15:07 Skoda Kylaq 1 Liter Manual Drive Impressions
19:51 Conclusion

Gaadify Article Link: https://gaadify.com/skoda-kylaq-review-highlights-from-our-test-drive/

Transparency Note:
